definition: individual/this/that/size/classifier for people or objects in general

sentences.english: All the mechanical parts been electroplated, he began to examine them one by one.
sentences.chinese: 所有的机械部件都电镀好以后，他开始逐个检查。

sentences.english: Do you think that autonomy is only the first step toward something else?
sentences.chinese: 你以为自治是独逐个个通向其他目的的第一步吗？

sentences.english: Trim toenails straight across using nail clippers.
sentences.chinese: 用指甲刀逐个修剪脚趾甲。

sentences.english: Please hand in your paper one by one.
Eg: He ticked the items one by one.
sentences.chinese: 他逐个在项目前面打钩。

sentences.english: I am traveling on in time in my review of these arguments.
sentences.chinese: 我正在依时间顺序逐个检视那些论点。

sentences.english: To test failover, stop the clones one by one.
sentences.chinese: 要测试故障转移，逐个地停止克隆。

sentences.english: A hundred millions of them laid down side by side would make a line only about an inch song.
sentences.chinese: 一亿个微粒逐个地排列成线，也只有大约一英寸长。

sentences.english: For the independent or vertical row of cross-pin, can be used individually embroidered embroidered France.
sentences.chinese: 对于独立或竖向并排的十字针，可采用逐个绣的绣法。

sentences.english: Today is the only day when I can bring myself to tell my wife I love her.
sentences.chinese: 今天是独逐个天我愿意跟老婆说我爱她的日子。

sentences.english: Why is the toilet, please listen to me on one one.
sentences.chinese: 为什么是厕所呢，请听我议逐个道来。

sentences.english: Further, you can configure unordered delivery on a stream-by-stream basis within an association.
sentences.chinese: 另外，您可以在一个联合中按照逐个流配置无序发送。

sentences.english: Filters in the chain do their processing one by one.
sentences.chinese: 链中的过滤器逐个执行其处理。

sentences.english: The solution of the whole team organization problem can be obtained by solving the sub-problems one by one.
sentences.chinese: 逐个解决子问题，即可获得整个团队组织问题的解。

sentences.english: Instead you output the information from the two feeds one after the other.
sentences.chinese: 作为替代方法，您可以逐个输出来自两个提要的信息。

sentences.english: The following sections examine these federated objects one by one.
sentences.chinese: 接下来的几个小节逐个研究这些联邦对象。

definition: one time (all the way through)/once through
